            <div class="help-title">Instructions</div>

            <div class="help-content">
                <ol>
                    <li>
                        Create the agent <code>scraping-challenge-5</code>
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        Access this page using <code>Puppeter.Page.goto()</code> and <code>Puppeter.Page.waitForSelector()</code>.
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        Use the function <code>buster.solveCaptchaBase64()</code> to resolve the image.
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        Use the functions <code>Puppeteer.Page.type()</code> and <code>Puppeteer.Page.click()</code> to fill the captcha solution and use <code>Puppeteer.Page.waitForSelector()</code> to make sure the data loaded.
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        Send the data using <code>buster.setResultObject()</code>.
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="help-title">Solution</div>

            <div class="help-content">
                <a href="/scripts/scraping-challenge-5.js">In case you are stuck</a>
            </div>
